01:04:49.610 --> 01:04:50.910
[ Laughter ]

01:04:50.910 --> 01:04:53.550
"Here he comes."

01:04:53.550 --> 01:04:54.850
[ Laughter ]

01:04:54.850 --> 01:05:00.150
"Here he comes."

01:05:00.150 --> 01:05:03.790
