01:05:03.790 --> 01:05:05.090
"Here he comes."

01:05:05.090 --> 01:05:06.390
[ Laughter ]

01:05:06.390 --> 01:05:08.360
"Here he comes.

01:05:08.360 --> 01:05:10.310
